This directory contains automated conformity tests for nRFgoStudio. The tests
work by automating nRFgoStudio's UI using AutoIt3[1] and WINE[2]. The tests
then generate output in TAP[3] format.

To run the tests, you can use any test harness supporting TAP, e.g. "prove"[4]:

$ cd tests/nrfgostudio/ && prove *.sh
default.sh .. ok   
All tests successful.
Files=1, Tests=1,  8 wallclock secs ( 0.04 usr  0.00 sys +  0.37 cusr  0.60 csys =  1.01 CPU)
Result: PASS

[1] http://www.autoitscript.com/site/autoit/
[2] http://www.winehq.org/
[3] http://testanything.org/tap-specification.html
[4] http://search.cpan.org/~leont/Test-Harness/bin/prove
